headline: Lamb Weston to Announce Fiscal Year 2026 Second Quarter Financial Results on December 19, 2025
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, November 19, 2025--Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) announced today it will report fiscal 2026 second quarter financial results on December 19, 2025. The news release will be issued at approximately 8:30 a.m. ET, followed by a conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET.

headline: 3 Reasons LW is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Lamb Weston has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small return of 4.7% while holding steady at $56.06. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 11.9% gain during that period.
